Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
gui_schematic_save_view(25.10)                  gui_schematic_save_view(25.10)

Name
       gui_schematic_save_view  -  Saves  the  current schematic view into the
       specified file

Syntax
       gui_schematic_save_view

       [-help]

       -file <file_name>

       [-name <string>]

       Saves the current schematic view into the specified file.

       This commands work only in the cone view (flattened mode).

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the  gui_schematic_save_view  com-
              mand.

              For  a detailed description of the command, use the man command:
              man gui_schematic_save_view.

       -file <file_name>
              Specifies the name of the file in which to  save  the  schematic
              view.

       -name <string>
              Specifies the name of the schematic view.

Related Information
              * gui_schematic_load_view

